.TH IFRAGGRAPH 1 "June 2026" "ilib @ILIB_VERSION@" "Ilib Manual"
.SH NAME
ifraggraph \- graph a player's frags from QuakeWorld frag logs
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ifraggraph
.I player
.I fraglog
.RI [ fraglog ...]
.B >
.I out.gif
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ifraggraph
parses one or more QuakeWorld frag log files and writes an image graphing the
named
.IR player 's
frag activity to standard output.
.PP
The
.I player
name is matched case-sensitively. If the player is not found in the logs the
tool reports the problem rather than crashing.
.SH EXAMPLES
.RS
.nf
ifraggraph "Player1" frag.log > player1.gif
.fi
.RE
.SH NOTES
This is a historical client tool retained as a worked example of using the
Ilib drawing and graphing API on parsed log data.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR iwebreprt (1)
.PP
Full API documentation: https://craigk5n.github.io/ilib/
